name: R00T in HSP1
description:
A translation into HSP1 by Hans Verhaegen of the essay “Root” by M Plummer-Fernández,  The embedded essay about fxhash and the growing interest in ecology-inspired gen art can be found within the generative series of root systems, also called “Root” available on fxhash: https://www.fxhash.xyz/generative/8867

See also NAJ in HSP: https://teia.art/objkt/27816
